Package nl.tue.fingerpaint.client.gui.buttons

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CancelCompareButton
    Button that can be used to cancel the comparing.
    CancelSaveResultsButton
    Button that resides on an save item panel to cancel the current save.
    CircleDrawingToolToggleButton
    ToggleButton that is used to select the circular drawing tool.
    CloseCompareButton
    Button that can be used to cancel the comparing.
    CloseLoadButton
    Button that can be used to close a panel in which "things" from the local storage can be selected.
    CloseResultsButton
    Button that can be used to close the remove results pop-up panel.
    CloseSaveButton
    Button that can be used to close the save results or overwrite pop-up panel.
    CloseSingleGraphViewButton
    Button that can be used to close the performance pop-up of a single graph.
    CompareButton
    Button that can be used to compare the performance of the selected mixing runs.
    ComparePerformanceButton
    Button that can be used to compare the performance of previously saved mixing runs.
    ExportDistributionButton
    Button that can be used to export a distribution.
    ExportMultipleGraphsButton
    Button that can be used to export multiple graphs.
    ExportSingleGraphButton
    Button that can be used to export the image of the current mixing performance.
    LoadInitDistButton
    Button that can be used to load a previously saved initial concentration distribution.
    LoadProtocolButton
    Button that can be used to load a protocol from the local storage.
    MenuToggleButton
    This button is used to show and hide the menu panel in the application.
    MixNowButton
    Button that can be used to execute the current mixing protocol.
    NewCompareButton
    Button that can be used to start a new comparison.
    OverwriteSaveButton
    Button that can be used to overwrite the item that is currently being saved.
    RemoveSavedResultsButton
    Button that can be used to remove previously saved mixing results.
    ResetDistButton
    Button to reset the current distribution to completely white.
    ResetProtocolButton
    Button to reset the current mixing protocol.
    SaveDistributionButton
    Button to save an initial concentration distribution.
    SaveItemPanelButton
    Button that can be used to actually initiate a saving action.
    SaveProtocolButton
    Button that can be used to save a mixing protocol.
    SaveResultsButton
    Button that can be used to save a mixing run.
    SquareDrawingToolToggleButton
    ToggleButton that is used to select the square drawing tool.
    ToggleColourButton
    Button that can be used to change the drawing colour.
    ToolSelectButton
    Button that can be used to change the drawing tool.
    ViewSingleGraphButton
    Button that can be used to view the performance of the previously executed mixing run in a single graph.
